        "content": "<p>brendandburns edited <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/6401\">PR #6401</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>This adds allow lists to HTTP which enable the creator of the wasm runtime to specify:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>allowed methods</li>\n<li>allowed schemes</li>\n<li>allowed authorities</li>\n</ul>\n<p>It also supports a wildcard value <code>*</code> which matches everything.</p>\n<p>Unit tests to validate the functionality are also included.</p>\n</blockquote>",
